# 1C MCP Workflow

- When editing .bsl: use both MCPs — 1c-help (spravka, snippets) and lsp-bsl-bridge (diagnostics, navigation)
- After edits: call `document_diagnostics` to verify
- When generating usable example code: call `save_1c_snippet` for future context
- URI for BSL LS in Docker: `file:///projects/<path>` (volume `.:/projects`, код обычно в `src`)
